sec.p:
The study is based on IPOs of common stock listed on BSE between June 1992 and March 2002. The sample selection is based on the following criteria:


The firm is listed on the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE);

The initial public offering is of common stock;

The initial public offering is from post-SEBI period and offered under free pricing era;

The firm has at least five years’ trading history from the date of its listing.
